SELECT sum("info_type"."id") as agg_0, avg("movie_info_idx"."info_type_id") as agg_1, sum("movie_info_idx"."info_type_id") as agg_2 FROM "info_type" LEFT OUTER JOIN "movie_info_idx" ON "info_type"."id" = "movie_info_idx"."info_type_id"  WHERE (CAST("movie_info_idx"."info" AS varchar) LIKE '%7%.6%' OR CAST("movie_info_idx"."info" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%7.8%') AND "movie_info_idx"."info_type_id" = 99 AND ("info_type"."id" >= 89 OR CAST("info_type"."info" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%dates%' OR "info_type"."id" <= 28);

SELECT "title"."series_years", max("title"."episode_nr") as agg_0, max("title"."season_nr" + "title"."episode_of_id") as agg_1, COUNT(*) as agg_2 FROM "movie_keyword" LEFT OUTER JOIN "title" ON "movie_keyword"."movie_id" = "title"."id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "keyword" ON "movie_keyword"."keyword_id" = "keyword"."id"  WHERE CAST("keyword"."phonetic_code" AS varchar) LIKE '%R165%2%' AND "movie_keyword"."id" >= 1347322 AND "movie_keyword"."movie_id" <= 1623614 GROUP BY "title"."series_years" ORDER BY "title"."series_years";

SELECT "info_type"."info", "title"."kind_id", avg("movie_info"."movie_id" + "title"."episode_nr") as agg_0 FROM "info_type" LEFT OUTER JOIN "movie_info_idx" ON "info_type"."id" = "movie_info_idx"."info_type_id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "title" ON "movie_info_idx"."movie_id" = "title"."id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "movie_info" ON "title"."id" = "movie_info"."movie_id"  WHERE "movie_info_idx"."id" <= 85693 AND CAST("info_type"."info" AS varchar) LIKE '%relea%se%' AND CAST("movie_info"."info" AS varchar) LIKE '%Spanish%' AND (CAST("info_type"."info" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%vote%s%' OR ("info_type"."id" <= 23 AND CAST("info_type"."info" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%gross%')) AND "title"."id" >= 1243834 GROUP BY "info_type"."info", "title"."kind_id" ORDER BY "info_type"."info", "title"."kind_id";

SELECT max("cast_info"."id" + "title"."production_year") as agg_0, sum("title"."episode_of_id") as agg_1, COUNT(*) as agg_2 FROM "movie_info_idx" LEFT OUTER JOIN "info_type" ON "movie_info_idx"."info_type_id" = "info_type"."id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "title" ON "movie_info_idx"."movie_id" = "title"."id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "kind_type" ON "title"."kind_id" = "kind_type"."id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "movie_info" ON "title"."id" = "movie_info"."movie_id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "cast_info" ON "title"."id" = "cast_info"."movie_id"  WHERE "kind_type"."kind" = 'tv series' AND "movie_info"."movie_id" >= 1080911 AND ("cast_info"."nr_order" BETWEEN 14.63771524376108 AND 163153579.41361055 OR "cast_info"."nr_order" <= 6.487527942470509 OR "cast_info"."nr_order" BETWEEN 0.7223611225316752 AND 8.930297806062509);

SELECT "movie_companies"."company_type_id", sum("movie_companies"."movie_id" + "movie_companies"."company_type_id") as agg_0, max("movie_companies"."company_id") as agg_1, max("movie_companies"."id" + "movie_companies"."movie_id") as agg_2 FROM "movie_companies"  WHERE ("movie_companies"."movie_id" BETWEEN 1499842 AND 2116594 OR "movie_companies"."id" >= 1837013) AND CAST("movie_companies"."note" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%(Hun%gary)%' GROUP BY "movie_companies"."company_type_id" ORDER BY "movie_companies"."company_type_id";

SELECT avg("char_name"."imdb_id" + "char_name"."id") as agg_0, min("char_name"."imdb_id") as agg_1 FROM "char_name"  WHERE "char_name"."imdb_index" = 'DM' AND "char_name"."id" BETWEEN 160317 AND 2938633 AND CAST("char_name"."name" AS varchar) LIKE '%Mr.%';

SELECT "title"."kind_id", "kind_type"."id", min("movie_info"."movie_id") as agg_0 FROM "kind_type" LEFT OUTER JOIN "title" ON "kind_type"."id" = "title"."kind_id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "movie_info_idx" ON "title"."id" = "movie_info_idx"."movie_id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "movie_info" ON "title"."id" = "movie_info"."movie_id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "cast_info" ON "title"."id" = "cast_info"."movie_id"  WHERE ("cast_info"."person_id" <= 1061337 OR "cast_info"."nr_order" <= 0.924658154537765) AND "movie_info_idx"."movie_id" <= 2240188 AND CAST("movie_info_idx"."info" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%7.7%' AND "kind_type"."id" = 1 GROUP BY "title"."kind_id", "kind_type"."id" ORDER BY "title"."kind_id", "kind_type"."id";

SELECT "cast_info"."role_id", sum("cast_info"."person_role_id") as agg_0, sum("title"."production_year" + "aka_name"."person_id") as agg_1 FROM "title" LEFT OUTER JOIN "cast_info" ON "title"."id" = "cast_info"."movie_id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "aka_name" ON "cast_info"."person_id" = "aka_name"."id"  WHERE (CAST("title"."title" AS varchar) LIKE '%of%' OR ("title"."id" BETWEEN 713595 AND 804153 AND CAST("title"."title" AS varchar) LIKE '%o%f%')) AND "cast_info"."movie_id" <= 1042998 AND CAST("cast_info"."note" AS varchar) LIKE '%Adle%r)%' AND ("title"."episode_nr" BETWEEN 9.324870225113791 AND 74854.85630034616 OR "title"."episode_nr" <= 3.980554753795973 OR "title"."episode_nr" <= 14.230144321343111) AND "cast_info"."id" BETWEEN 13265295 AND 21247535 GROUP BY "cast_info"."role_id" ORDER BY "cast_info"."role_id";

SELECT "info_type"."info", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "info_type" LEFT OUTER JOIN "movie_info_idx" ON "info_type"."id" = "movie_info_idx"."info_type_id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "title" ON "movie_info_idx"."movie_id" = "title"."id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "cast_info" ON "title"."id" = "cast_info"."movie_id"  WHERE "movie_info_idx"."movie_id" BETWEEN 567294 AND 1993407 AND CAST("title"."title" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%to%' GROUP BY "info_type"."info" ORDER BY "info_type"."info";

SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "title" LEFT OUTER JOIN "cast_info" ON "title"."id" = "cast_info"."movie_id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "movie_info" ON "title"."id" = "movie_info"."movie_id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "char_name" ON "cast_info"."person_role_id" = "char_name"."id"  WHERE "cast_info"."movie_id" <= 106207 AND CAST("cast_info"."note" AS varchar) LIKE '%(%archive%' AND ("movie_info"."id" >= 7343979 OR (CAST("movie_info"."info" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%Portugues%e%' AND "movie_info"."id" >= 8549566));

SELECT min("cast_info"."movie_id") as agg_0 FROM "cast_info" LEFT OUTER JOIN "aka_name" ON "cast_info"."person_id" = "aka_name"."id"  WHERE CAST("aka_name"."name_pcode_cf" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%A5362%' AND "cast_info"."movie_id" >= 2397248 AND CAST("cast_info"."note" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%(a%s%' AND ("cast_info"."person_role_id" BETWEEN 282103.9551513621 AND 2742000.3054621443 OR ("cast_info"."person_role_id" <= 466641.48319293227 AND "cast_info"."person_role_id" >= 90487.64430575298));

SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0, avg("title"."episode_nr" + "movie_info_idx"."note") as agg_1 FROM "title" LEFT OUTER JOIN "movie_info_idx" ON "title"."id" = "movie_info_idx"."movie_id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "info_type" ON "movie_info_idx"."info_type_id" = "info_type"."id"  WHERE "info_type"."info" = 'nick names' AND "title"."imdb_id" != 'F624';

SELECT "title"."imdb_index", max("cast_info"."person_id") as agg_0, sum("movie_info"."info_type_id") as agg_1 FROM "movie_info" LEFT OUTER JOIN "title" ON "movie_info"."movie_id" = "title"."id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "cast_info" ON "title"."id" = "cast_info"."movie_id"  WHERE CAST("title"."title" AS varchar) LIKE '%T%he%' AND CAST("cast_info"."note" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%(uncredite%d)%' GROUP BY "title"."imdb_index" ORDER BY "title"."imdb_index";

SELECT "title"."imdb_id", "company_type"."id", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "company_type" LEFT OUTER JOIN "movie_companies" ON "company_type"."id" = "movie_companies"."company_type_id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "company_name" ON "movie_companies"."company_id" = "company_name"."id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "title" ON "movie_companies"."movie_id" = "title"."id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "cast_info" ON "title"."id" = "cast_info"."movie_id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "movie_keyword" ON "title"."id" = "movie_keyword"."movie_id"  WHERE "company_name"."country_code" != '[hr]' AND "movie_keyword"."id" BETWEEN 1321145 AND 2697015 GROUP BY "title"."imdb_id", "company_type"."id" ORDER BY "title"."imdb_id", "company_type"."id";

SELECT "cast_info"."role_id", min("cast_info"."nr_order") as agg_0 FROM "cast_info"  WHERE ("cast_info"."nr_order" <= 1.8269582834114062 OR "cast_info"."role_id" BETWEEN 1 AND 2 OR "cast_info"."nr_order" <= 3.2912008991968014) AND "cast_info"."id" <= 10849659 AND "cast_info"."person_role_id" >= 1293291.7027913467 AND "cast_info"."movie_id" >= 2499280 GROUP BY "cast_info"."role_id" ORDER BY "cast_info"."role_id";

SELECT "title"."imdb_index", avg("title"."id" + "cast_info"."person_role_id") as agg_0, avg("movie_companies"."id" + "title"."episode_of_id") as agg_1 FROM "title" LEFT OUTER JOIN "movie_companies" ON "title"."id" = "movie_companies"."movie_id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "cast_info" ON "title"."id" = "cast_info"."movie_id"  WHERE "title"."id" >= 1090576 AND "cast_info"."person_id" BETWEEN 1133507 AND 3984243 GROUP BY "title"."imdb_index" ORDER BY "title"."imdb_index";

SELECT "company_name"."country_code", "cast_info"."role_id", max("title"."season_nr") as agg_0 FROM "company_name" LEFT OUTER JOIN "movie_companies" ON "company_name"."id" = "movie_companies"."company_id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "title" ON "movie_companies"."movie_id" = "title"."id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "cast_info" ON "title"."id" = "cast_info"."movie_id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "kind_type" ON "title"."kind_id" = "kind_type"."id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "movie_info" ON "title"."id" = "movie_info"."movie_id"  WHERE "cast_info"."person_id" BETWEEN 2686320 AND 2860146 AND "cast_info"."person_role_id" BETWEEN 45489.12598255127 AND 329217.7480489494 AND CAST("company_name"."country_code" AS varchar) LIKE '%[in]%' AND "kind_type"."id" >= 2 AND "cast_info"."movie_id" BETWEEN 475952 AND 1325661 GROUP BY "company_name"."country_code", "cast_info"."role_id" ORDER BY "company_name"."country_code", "cast_info"."role_id";

SELECT "name"."gender", "aka_name"."imdb_index", min("aka_name"."person_id") as agg_0, min("person_info"."person_id") as agg_1 FROM "person_info" LEFT OUTER JOIN "name" ON "person_info"."person_id" = "name"."id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "aka_name" ON "name"."id" = "aka_name"."person_id"  WHERE "aka_name"."person_id" <= 3462576 AND (CAST("name"."surname_pcode" AS varchar) LIKE '%A5%3%' OR CAST("name"."surname_pcode" AS varchar) LIKE '%A%25%') AND "person_info"."info_type_id" BETWEEN 21 AND 25 AND "name"."imdb_id" IS NOT NULL AND "name"."gender" IN ('f') GROUP BY "name"."gender", "aka_name"."imdb_index" ORDER BY "name"."gender", "aka_name"."imdb_index";

SELECT max("movie_keyword"."keyword_id") as agg_0, sum("title"."episode_of_id" + "keyword"."id") as agg_1, sum("keyword"."id" + "title"."episode_of_id") as agg_2 FROM "movie_keyword" LEFT OUTER JOIN "keyword" ON "movie_keyword"."keyword_id" = "keyword"."id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "title" ON "movie_keyword"."movie_id" = "title"."id"  WHERE "keyword"."id" >= 51817;
